      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Skies are Gray",
        "Client": "Energetic Fisherwoman",
        "Description": "When the skies cloud over, ya think\r\nthere\u0027s rain on the way, don\u0027tcha?\r\nWell, this time, it weren\u0027t no storm,\r\nit was a dang Tobi-Kadachi! Can\u0027t do\r\nno fishin\u0027 when you\u0027re gettin\u0027 zapped\r\nin the rear every other minute! I want\r\nthat varmint gone, ya hear me!?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "\u00C7a commence \u00E0 se couvrir...",
        "Client": "P\u00EAcheuse \u00E9nergique",
        "Description": "Quand \u00E7a se couvre on s\u0027attend \u00E0\r\nc\u0027qu\u0027il pleuve... Sauf que c\u0027\u00E9tait\r\npas la m\u00E9t\u00E9o, c\u0027\u00E9tait un\r\nTobi-Kadachi ! J\u0027risque pas d\u0027p\u00EAcher\r\navec c\u0027te vermine qui m\u0027colle aux\r\nbasques ! J\u0027compte sur toi\r\npour lui donner une bonne racl\u00E9e !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Il cielo \u00E8 grigio",
        "Client": "Pescatrice energica",
        "Description": "Quando si addensano le nuvole,\r\ndi solito poi piove, no? Beh,\r\nstavolta, invece del temporale\r\n\u00E8 apparso un Tobi-Kadachi! Non\r\nsi pu\u00F2 pescare ricevendo\r\nscosse in ogni istante. Caccia\r\nquel mascalzone, hai capito?!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Grauer Himmel",
        "Client": "Energische Fischerin",
        "Description": "Wenn Wolken aufziehen, bedeutet\r\ndas Regen, stimmt\u0027s? Tja, diesmal\r\nwar\u0027s kein Sturm, sondern \u0027n ver-\r\ndammter Tobi-Kadachi! Is\u0027 nix mit\r\nangeln, wenn du st\u00E4ndig von hinten\r\neinen gewischt kriegst! Ich will, dass\r\ndie Plage verschwindet, h\u00F6rst du?!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Tobi-Kadachi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Amenaza a\u00E9rea",
        "Client": "Pescadora energ\u00E9tica",
        "Description": "Cuando el cielo se encapota,\r\ndir\u00EDas que va a llover, \u00BFno?\r\nPues esta vez no es el tiempo,\r\n\u00A1sino un Tobi-Kadachi!\r\nNo podemos dormir, pescar ni\r\ncomerciar as\u00ED, \u00A1no hasta que\r\nesa alima\u00F1a haya ca\u00EDdo!",
        "Target": "Caza un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0421\u0435\u0440\u044B\u0435 \u043D\u0435\u0431\u0435\u0441\u0430",
        "Client": "\u0411\u043E\u0439\u043A\u0430\u044F \u0440\u044B\u0431\u0430\u0447\u043A\u0430",
        "Description": "\u041A\u043E\u0433\u0434\u0430 \u0441\u043E\u0431\u0438\u0440\u0430\u044E\u0442\u0441\u044F \u0442\u0443\u0447\u0438, \u043C\u043E\u0436\u043D\u043E\r\n\u0440\u0435\u0448\u0438\u0442\u044C, \u0447\u0442\u043E \u0431\u0443\u0434\u0435\u0442 \u0434\u043E\u0436\u0434\u044C,\r\n\u0432\u0435\u0440\u043D\u043E? \u041D\u043E \u044D\u0442\u043E \u0431\u044B\u043B \u043D\u0435 \u0434\u043E\u0436\u0434\u044C \u2014\r\n\u0422\u043E\u0431\u0438-\u041A\u0430\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0438! \u041D\u0435\u0432\u043E\u0437\u043C\u043E\u0436\u043D\u043E\r\n\u0440\u044B\u0431\u0430\u0447\u0438\u0442\u044C, \u043A\u043E\u0433\u0434\u0430 \u0442\u0435\u0431\u044F \u0432\u0441\u0435\r\n\u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F \u0431\u044C\u044E\u0442 \u0442\u043E\u043A\u043E\u043C! \u0420\u0430\u0437\u0431\u0435\u0440\u0438\u0441\u044C\r\n\u0441 \u044D\u0442\u0438\u043C \u0432\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043B\u0435\u043C!",
